# Walkthrough: Vehicle Damage Detection Modular Pipeline

## What Was Built

A complete, modular end-to-end pipeline for vehicle damage detection with **46 source files** across 9 components. The core design goal — **strategy swappability** — is achieved through a model registry + strategy pattern that lets you swap model architectures via YAML config changes alone.

## Architecture Summary

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["YAML Config"] --> B["Model Registry"]
    B --> C["Trainer (Model-Agnostic)"]
    A --> C
    A --> D["Data Pipeline"]
    D --> C
    C --> E["Callbacks"]
    C --> F["Evaluator"]
    F --> G["Comparator"]
    C --> H["Checkpoints"]
